{"tid":1161262,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"麥巴比32球金靴獎追貼美斯","createTime":"2019-05-19T05:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T06:17:05.000Z","uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ad08cb38b76dd52ecaf69461a7ce9e3278a7ebd2","tid":1161262,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:09:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=25578183291\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D25578183291&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPQ5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=dc792a11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=25578183291</a><br />\n【Now Sports-體育】基利安麥巴比在周六法甲射入兩球，成為逾半世紀以來法甲入球最多的法國球員，而他在歐洲金靴獎爭奪上已力逼美斯。<br />\n<br />\n巴黎聖日耳門在上周六主場對迪安之戰，憑基利安麥巴比（Kylian Mbappe）梅開二度大勝4:0，這位停賽刑滿的鋒將賽後累積32個入球，成為1967年以來首位法國球員在法甲單季入球達到此數目，即逾半世紀以來第一人。<br />\n<br />\n他在歐洲金靴獎的爭奪上逼近巴塞隆拿的美斯，後者目前以34球領先。麥巴比的PSG尚餘一場下周作客對蘭斯的比賽，而美斯所屬的巴塞隆拿，於周日西甲煞科戰作客對伊巴。<br />\n<br />\nPSG亦在這場本季主場謝幕戰正式獲頒較早前已鎖定的法甲冠軍，現場大放煙花，氣氛熾熱。<br />\n<br />\n此外，另一傳統勁旅摩納哥主場以2:0打敗艾米恩斯，比排尾3需要踢護級附加賽的卡昂多3分，且在得失球差領先後者7球，基本上已護級成功。"},{"pid":"bcaa625d0afe1f0e9e3fd5a3c0791c588c17bdd6","tid":1161262,"uid":50745,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:10:58.000Z","msg":"法甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2629a2af05cf542adb8c0c1263338f2dd5c883","tid":1161262,"uid":192409,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:11:55.000Z","msg":"法甲入一球2分<br />\n英超西甲入一球又2分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208d2445b031d380676096e5d1596bde89048beb","tid":1161262,"uid":18569,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:17:21.000Z","msg":"包皮點同美斯玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf81c48924411c8df04f5c677d6dd538b8aa5d4","tid":1161262